# Warriors (Agnostic Front album)

}}
Warriors is the ninth full-length studio album from New York hardcore band Agnostic Front released on November 6, 2007.[https://www.amazon.com/Warriors-Agnostic-Front/dp/B000W03RI0 Amazon.com: Warriors: Music: Agnostic Front]
The album is produced by Madball frontman Freddy Cricien, who is the half-brother of Agnostic Front frontman Roger Miret.
